Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.03,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It's... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.78,0:00:33.13,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Touko!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.55,0:00:34.90,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.90,0:00:35.80,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.45,0:00:37.60,Glasslip-Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,Touko!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.45,0:00:37.60,Glasslip-Alt,Everyone,0,0,0,,Touko-san?!{her family says touko while kakeru's family says touko-san so put both these in}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.76,0:00:50.86,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.19,0:00:56.06,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'll let them in.{i'll bring them over.}{i like the line that's there already}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.68,0:01:00.89,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Don't go.{thanks cr}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.82,0:01:09.06,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.06,0:01:10.20,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.20,0:01:15.22,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I wanted to hear your mother's piano too.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.78,0:01:18.21,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I didn't hear any fragments.{i wanna phrase this like, "no sounds came to me" to show he's talking about the fragments specifically}{This should do it}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.21,0:01:22.04,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,But whatever you saw\Nmade you lose consciousness.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.04,0:01:24.34,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Does this mean that our\Nexperiment was a success?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.34,0:01:25.37,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.01,0:01:29.69,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,But I also put you in serious danger.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.05,0:01:31.89,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm totally fine, though!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.89,0:01:32.92,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.50,0:01:41.55,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Whenever I'm around people,\NI only get them involved in my problems.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.84,0:01:44.79,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Touko?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.51,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.51,0:01:50.89,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I want to stay here a bit longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.89,0:01:51.38,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.50,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,O-Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.50,0:01:57.36,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Maybe it'd be best if you\Nrested here for a while longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.36,0:01:59.92,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I want to make some more\Nglass beads when I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.92,0:02:01.35,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.68,0:02:18.05,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Are you sure we shouldn't have brought her home with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.16,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.26,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Still... I wonder what happened to her.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.26,0:02:24.39,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Yes, what indeed?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.41,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,She's quite mature now, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.41,0:02:27.73,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.73,0:02:29.99,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Are you saying that I'm still just a kid?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.99,0:02:32.30,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Hina. You'll be an adult soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.75,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Before you even know it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.26,Glasslip-Main,Mum,0,0,0,,Oh? Another piece?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.61,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.97,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'll head home right afterward.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.26,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Are you sure you'll be okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.26,0:02:45.80,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.69,0:02:48.11,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Excuse me, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.11,0:02:49.81,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Could you play a really dramatic one?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.78,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.02,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.02,0:03:01.78,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why should I be? Those aren't glimpses of the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.83,0:03:06.74,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}But still, Kakeru-kun is sure to be...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.21,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's sure to be gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.26,Glasslip-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.40,0:03:25.18,Glasslip-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,I must say, I never thought I'd see you\Nall gathered here to order some Mandheling.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.45,0:03:32.43,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I'm kinda nervous all of a sudden. I wonder why?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.43,0:03:34.52,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Yeah, I feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.41,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,It's bitter.{LIKE YOUR TEARS, HIRO}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.53,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I bet it'd be brighter\Nif Touko-san were here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.53,0:03:50.08,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,We used to meet up at this place every so often by chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.20,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I should give her a call.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.02,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.42,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I'd prefer for us to meet by chance again.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.88,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You can sound pretty cool when you want to.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.25,0:04:03.77,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Yeah, sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.88,0:04:12.06,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Sorry. I went and stirred things up.{this is like an unintentional pun.}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.65,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'll tell you and Sachi about it too, Hiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.52,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.89,0:04:17.60,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.60,0:04:20.76,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Everyone has their secrets.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.79,0:04:24.99,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,J-Just a few small ones, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.93,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I guess it's because we're all\Nhere together, drinking coffee.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.53,0:05:00.73,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.73,0:05:01.52,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.62,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.57,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.51,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.51,0:05:10.75,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,She's already in the studio again?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.75,0:05:11.55,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.08,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.49,0:05:16.66,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,She came in here, panicking about her unfinished summer homework.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.19,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Leave her to it, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.59,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.66,0:05:25.03,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, Hina. It says here there'll be a meteor shower tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.81,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,That takes me back to another\Nmeteor shower we had in the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.81,0:05:31.14,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Your mother told me that\Nshe wanted to see the stars,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.68,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,so I made up my mind\Nto propose to her that night.{mari-your mother? this is way back to like ep 1 or something i dont remember her name}{let's. and yeah, it's her mother}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.91,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Dad, your newspaper's in my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.61,0:06:00.53,Glasslip-Main,Kakerudad,0,0,0,,Kakeru,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.95,Glasslip-Main,Kakerudad,0,0,0,,have you decided what you'll do?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.95,0:06:04.61,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.15,0:06:08.59,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,You're a grown man now.{i know, almost != a, but this sounds a lot better and agrees with 92}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.59,0:06:13.98,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,You get to do what you want to,\Nand I'll be supporting you the best I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.65,0:06:17.02,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You were really strict\Nwith me back in middle school.{You gave me a hard time while I was in middle school.}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.50,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Middle schoolers are kids,\Nbut high schoolers are adults.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.50,0:06:23.76,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,I believed in that weird distinction.{maybe "It sounds weird, but that's where I draw the line."}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.87,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Something like that, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.91,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I've noticed you're still hiking.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.40,0:06:32.78,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I don't really climb up.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.72,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I walk around the foothills for half a day or so.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.46,0:06:39.45,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,You weren't keen at all when\NI first invited you to come with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.45,0:06:42.02,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah. Well, I am now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.89,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we've gone together.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.89,0:06:47.26,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You think you'd be able\Nto keep up with me, Dad?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.30,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Is that a challenge?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.65,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Honey, come give me a hand!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.81,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'll answer it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.85,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.16,0:06:57.98,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.84,0:06:59.35,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Takayama?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.96,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Let's take a break here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.18,0:07:28.41,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I heard from Hina-chan that your mother\Nheld a piano concert at your home.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.53,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I wouldn't call it a "concert".
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.26,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Just a little gathering of sorts.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.62,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You should invite me too for your next one.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.57,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Takayama—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.57,0:07:37.43,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Yanagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.13,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You can call me Yanagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.86,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Do you like classical music, Yanagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.44,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I listen to it a lot, actually.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.45,0:08:05.37,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I love the black tea that you make, Mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.20,0:08:07.25,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Thank you, dear.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.88,0:08:12.18,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Say, Touko, whenever you\Nget blinded by a bright light,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.86,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,you don't happen to see\Nsomething hazy, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.86,0:08:15.51,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.01,0:08:20.24,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,When I was young, I would see\Nthings like that from time to time,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.24,0:08:25.52,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,and at one point I thought they might be glimpses into my own future.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.73,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,But as it turned out, I was wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.45,0:08:34.33,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,My actual future was filled with things I'd never even dreamed of.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.33,0:08:37.03,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,I still wonder what those visions were.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.26,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Do they give you direction?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.42,0:08:42.44,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.44,0:08:45.42,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But it's the best I can do for the moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.39,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.34,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,You've gotta make the most of now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.21,0:08:50.94,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yup!
Comment: 10,0:08:53.76,0:08:57.26,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,eyecatch
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.76,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I'm calling in your promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.73,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I'll be happy to remind you if you've forgotten.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.23,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,No, I remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.95,0:09:06.94,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,There's only one promise I made with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.54,0:09:11.47,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Wanna join us?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.61,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,You can tell me later.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.61,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I got the gist of it from Sachi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.76,0:09:20.58,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.60,0:09:24.58,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,The incident at the beach that led to our promise
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.09,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,and Touko's fainting a few days ago
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.08,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,were both my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.95,0:09:34.02,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,How much of that am I\Nsupposed to believe to be true?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.31,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I don't think I can bring myself to accept every word you say.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.62,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Believe whatever you want, but it's all true.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.62,0:09:43.18,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,It's also true that I needed Touko to be with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.17,0:09:47.85,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,However, if I didn't exist, Touko wouldn't have been hurt the way she was.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.83,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} hurt Touko.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.56,0:09:54.28,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I can't even begin to imagine what it was that Touko saw.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.50,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,It's not always good, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.49,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,To come to a realization, that is.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.18,0:10:03.70,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.70,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Do you mean Imi Yukinari?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.62,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.42,0:10:14.46,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Even if he doesn't say a word,\NI know exactly what's on his mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.47,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,That sounds like quite a nuisance indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.72,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.35,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Kakeru, are you going to disappear?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.08,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,It kinda feels like you will.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.18,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving now!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.18,0:10:31.66,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.58,0:10:35.92,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Where's she going\Nthis late in the evening?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.92,0:10:36.69,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.47,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,She seemed really pumped, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.61,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Where's Onee-chan off to?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.10,0:10:44.08,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,My, everyone's so worried about {\i1}Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.11,0:11:29.41,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.09,0:11:30.96,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Touko.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.30,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I join you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.78,0:11:42.72,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.22,0:11:54.52,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,There's going to be a meteor shower tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.52,0:11:57.04,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if we could see it as clearly as the fireworks.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.11,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I hope we'll be able to see\Nthe fireworks together next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.67,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,This cloudy sky doesn't look promising.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.77,0:12:04.87,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Winter fireworks...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.99,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Huh? Winter?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.73,0:12:12.12,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,In the fragment of the future I saw,\Neveryone was going to see the fireworks in winter.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.56,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,And you went to see them?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.56,0:12:14.43,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.51,0:12:16.97,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I watched them alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.01,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,What about everyone else?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.87,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,They didn't recognize me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.93,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.34,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You watched them by yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.57,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,That was the first time\NI'd watched fireworks alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.52,0:12:34.85,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,That was {\i1}my{\i0} sudden but\Nforeseeable loneliness, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.80,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I would have liked to have seen those fireworks with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.55,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You were there too, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.50,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,With everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.35,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Was that "me" having fun?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.35,0:12:46.40,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yes, very much so.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.74,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.16,0:12:53.27,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What are these "fragments of the future", after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.27,0:12:56.58,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,That's probably not the best name for them at this point.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.18,0:12:59.70,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,My mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.35,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.01,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Actually, never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.75,0:13:04.23,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.90,0:13:08.44,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I was just thinking you'd started saying "never mind" again.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.08,0:13:14.48,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,But you say that whenever it's about\Nsomething important to you, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.47,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Am I that easy to read?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.47,0:13:19.77,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.11,0:13:20.99,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.89,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.62,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Something important to me...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.62,0:13:28.03,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,That day, at the fireworks display, I saw you, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.34,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Was that just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.34,0:13:31.69,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.04,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I refuse to believe it could be.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.38,0:13:37.06,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You saw me that day because\Nyou {\i1}wanted{\i0} to see me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.73,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,That wasn't the future I saw.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.73,0:13:45.81,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It was something that hadn't happened yet,\Nbut which would happen eventually...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.67,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Hang on, isn't that the same thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.90,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Do you think it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.90,0:13:54.27,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Um... no.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.85,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Then, it's not the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.14,0:14:03.45,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.64,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you, Touko.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.11,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,And that's the reason we did?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.89,0:14:13.79,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'm sure the bright lights and sounds of\Nthe fireworks at that moment made it happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.79,0:14:16.66,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It sure was loud and bright, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.09,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But why us?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.09,0:14:23.96,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Even in the world with the winter fireworks,\NI wasn't able to do anything for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.96,0:14:28.16,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I feel like all I accomplished was to\Nunderstand a little more about how you feel.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.82,0:14:29.84,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But I didn't get to...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.75,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I didn't get to do anything for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.64,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You've accomplished more than enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.30,0:14:37.76,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.05,0:14:41.14,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'm glad I got to meet you, in this town.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.76,0:14:46.45,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm glad you came to this town, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.71,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,We can't see the stars...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.06,0:14:53.78,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.66,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,We can make these our stars.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.67,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You made all of those?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.50,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.45,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.53,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Ready, set...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.57,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Shooting stars...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.57,0:15:53.76,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.89,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Can you see them too, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.89,0:15:56.76,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.04,0:16:10.77,Glasslip-Main,TV,0,0,0,,This year's meteor shower will be unusually active.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.77,0:16:14.53,Glasslip-Main,TV,0,0,0,,The Kappa Cygnids meteor shower reaches its peak tonight,{We may be able to see the Cygnus constellation at its finest as the meteors grace the night sky,}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.53,0:16:18.41,Glasslip-Main,TV,0,0,0,,but unfortunately, due to cloudy skies across all regions—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.33,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I wanted to see them, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.65,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.39,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I can see them!
Comment: 10,0:16:28.39,0:16:28.82,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Eh?{probably no need to sub this}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.82,0:16:29.46,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.51,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,You can?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.34,0:16:48.82,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,That was...
Comment: 10,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.18,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Hm?{same}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.99,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,a beautiful proposal.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.26,0:16:58.79,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Right from the moment we met—our first date,\Neverything—you were so unbelievably earnest
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.45,0:17:02.83,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,that I completely fell for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.94,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Why is only Jonathan called "Jonathan"?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.79,0:17:37.54,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yuki-kun, are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.54,0:17:39.92,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,The late summer heat\Nhasn't gotten to you, has it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.12,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.69,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,All the other chickens are\Nnamed after philosophers!{... guess one of them was Marx after all.}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.57,0:17:46.25,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.65,0:17:48.50,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Then what about "Jonathan"?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.94,0:17:51.25,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,The name of an adventurer, maybe?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.90,0:17:55.26,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hang on, you've been sketching them this whole time and you didn't know?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.66,0:17:58.02,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.56,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Our summer break will be over soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.12,0:18:05.14,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,From here on,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.78,0:18:12.06,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I hope that I'll be able to handle\Nwhatever the future has in store for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.69,0:18:16.53,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Man, you never change.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.91,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Or have you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.64,Glasslip-Main,Girls,0,0,0,,He's gotten back into it lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.73,Glasslip-Main,Girls,0,0,0,,Oh, here he comes!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.73,0:18:52.86,Glasslip-Main,Girls,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.86,0:18:53.72,Glasslip-Main,Girls,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.72,0:18:54.57,Glasslip-Main,Girls,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.69,Glasslip-Main,Girls,0,0,0,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.20,Glasslip-Main,Girls,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.28,Glasslip-Main,Girls,0,0,0,,Where's Hina?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.36,0:19:03.28,Glasslip-Main,Girls,0,0,0,,Hey, Hina, tell us what's going on!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.24,Glasslip-Alt,Girls,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.30,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,There's the focus knob.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.44,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.44,0:19:24.97,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.24,0:19:32.48,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I think "Touko" is a beautiful name.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.89,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.57,0:19:38.08,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,But I think "Hiro" is a beautiful name too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.30,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,C-Can I help you with anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.30,0:19:48.49,Glasslip-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,You're a customer too for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.15,Glasslip-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.67,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, why're you so late?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.97,0:20:18.57,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Is she still going to make it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.28,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.69,0:20:26.49,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Unlike you, Sis, this young man's summer break is over.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.92,0:20:29.10,Glasslip-Main,Sis,0,0,0,,You're up already. How strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.08,Glasslip-Main,Sis,0,0,0,,Something exciting happen to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.34,0:20:36.63,Glasslip-Main,Sis,0,0,0,,Could the fragile glasses girl be back at school?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.51,0:20:38.96,Glasslip-Main,Sis,0,0,0,,Well, good for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.76,Glasslip-Main,Sis,0,0,0,,How about a celebratory ride in my car?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.46,0:20:46.34,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,The only way I'm going to be\Nlate to school is if you drive me there.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.80,Glasslip-Main,Momo,0,0,0,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.74,0:20:56.44,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I guess all that jogging paid off.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.93,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'll be going now!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.93,0:21:13.66,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.10,0:21:15.06,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.63,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Watch out for cars, girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.31,Glasslip-Main,GirlA,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.90,0:21:45.57,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Touko!
