Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.58,0:19:19.47,IN01-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}itsumono keshiki ga fui ni chigatte mieta
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.47,0:19:29.56,IN01-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}konna natsu wa nido to konaitte kizuita no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.56,0:19:45.70,IN01-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}toumei na hitomi no oku wazuka ni hajiketa niji no kakera
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.70,0:19:55.38,IN01-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}kagayaki dasu shinkirou no mukou gawa
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.38,0:20:00.67,IN01-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}te wo nobase ba ashita ga hora,
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.89,IN01-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}kawaru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:45.77,IN01-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}I listen to the sound of the waves as I walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:55.07,IN01-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Thoughts about the things ahead of us never crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:19:02.41,IN01-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}All that mattered to me was the time we spent laughing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:11.58,IN01-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}I turn around as the wind from behind sweeps past me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:19.47,IN01-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}and the scenery in front of me suddenly looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:29.56,IN01-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}I realize a summer like this will never come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:45.70,IN01-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}An array of colors burst and shatter in the distance beyond these clear beads.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:55.38,IN01-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}They shine brightly in the mirage {I see }on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:20:00.67,IN01-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}See, if you just try to reach out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.89,IN01-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}you can change your future.
