Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.48,0:22:32.24,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(250,250)\be1}I pondered over the sound of waves astir in my heart
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.24,0:22:40.29,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(250,250)\be1}though the rays of the sun blinded me from the truth.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.38,0:22:49.84,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(250,250)\be1}Just like the pictures I drew in my diary as a child,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.84,0:22:58.68,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(250,250)\be1}everything around us is being immersed in color.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.68,0:23:03.77,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(250,250)\be1}I try to close my eyes and hide
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.77,0:23:07.65,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(250,250)\be1}from the brilliant blue sea and sky,
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.65,0:23:12.57,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(250,250)\be1}but your voice always finds its way
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.57,0:23:21.00,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(250,250)\be1}right into the corners of my heart and holds on tight.
